Alumni portal - allows alumni to register and provides search.

Javascript UI using Knockout.js with REST-like services using Rails 3, MongoDb (1.8.1), Solr

rvm gemset create alumni_portal
rvm gemset use alumni_portal
bundle install
start Mongo DB process: <MONGO_HOME>/bin/mongod --dbpath=
rake sunspot:solr:start
rails server
Open http://localhost:3000 in a browser.